Class GameManager

java.lang.Object
logic.GameManager
public class GameManager extends Object
This class manages the game state, including money, inventory, perks, and the game loop.

  • Method Details

    • processGameLoop

      public void processGameLoop()
      Called Perk Method to Decrements perk timers/cooldowns. Calculates passive income from generators (applying multipliers and perks) and adds it to current money.

    • clickCookie

      public void clickCookie()
      Adds money based on clickPower. Doubles the amount if Click Perk is active.
